artiest.Name: Linkin Park
artiest.Description: Linkin Park is an American rock band from Agoura Hills, California.

artiest.Name: Green Day
artiest.Description: Green Day is an American punk rock band formed in 1987.

artiest.Name: Stromae
artiest.Description: Paul Van Haver, better known as Stromae is a Belgian singer-songwriter. He has distinguished himself in both hip hop and electronic music. One of his topsongs is papadouie.

artiest.Name: Adele
artiest.Description: Adele Laurie Blue Adkins MBE, better known simply as Adele, is an English singer, songwriter, musician, and multi-instrumentalist.

artiest.Name: Martin Garrix
artiest.Description: Martijn Garritsen, known by his stage name Martin Garrix, is a Dutch DJ signed to Spinnin' Records. This year's hitlist haven been bombed by his new song: 'animals'.

artiest.Name: Sam Gooris
artiest.Description: In 1989 werd de toen zestienjarige Sam Gooris Belgisch Kampioen Soundmix met een imitatie van Shakin' Stevens. Zijn echte debuut in de muziekwereld begint na de oprichting van VTM. Hij kwam in aanraking met Jack Rivers, een manager die onder meer al Wendy Van Wanten en Jo Vally een platencontract aanbood.

artiest.Name: Arctic Monkeys
artiest.Description: Arctic Monkeys are an English indie rock band formed in 2002 in High Green, a suburb of Sheffield. The band consists of Alex Turner, Jamie Cook, Nick O'Malley, and Matt Helders.

artiest.Name: Martin Garrix
artiest.Description: Martijn Garritsen, known by his stage name Martin Garrix, is a Dutch DJ signed to Spinnin' Records. This year's hitlist haven been bombed by his new song: 'animals'.
